{"product_id":"madara-spot-roll-on-8ml","title":"MÁDARA Spot Roll-On 8ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis powerful, concentrated solution attacks blemishes on contact. Juniper Stem Cells and Salicylic Acid instantly get spots under control. Invisible to the skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply directly to blemishes. Reapply after 2 hours if necessary. For external use only. Keep out of the eye and lip area. For best results, use in combination with the rest of ACNE solutions.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Alcohol, Aqua, Salicylic Acid, Ilex Paraguariensis (Mate) Leaf Extract, Potassium Hydroxide, Cetraria Islandica (Iceland Moss) Extract, Usnea Barbata (Lichen) Extract, Juniperus Communis (Juniper) Callus Culture Extract\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49888025837895,"sku":null,"price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-spot-roll-on-8ml-692861.jpg?v=1739897262","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/madara-spot-roll-on-8ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}